Information
------------------------------

The House Of Hypochondriacs
Dr Christian Jessen invites three people with health anxiety to meet others living with the conditions they fear most, in a bid to relieve their hypochondria. The trio are also enlightened to the reality of overstretched NHS resources by visiting a GP practice and ambulance service, whose work is increased by self-diagnosing individuals, who are often misguided by internet advice.
